pipeline_summary.name: query_sales_data_pipeline
pipeline_summary.description: Sequential linear pipeline that generates daily sales reports by querying PostgreSQL sales data, converting it to CSV, creating a PDF chart, and emailing the report to management.

components.name: Query Sales Data
components.description: Extracts daily aggregated sales data from the PostgreSQL sales table using the execution date as a filter.
outputs: Aggregated sales data by date and product (table)

upstream_policy.description: First step in the linear pipeline; no upstream dependencies.

components.name: Transform Sales Data to CSV
components.description: Converts the extracted aggregated sales data into a CSV file using pandas.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful execution of query_sales_data.

components.name: Generate PDF Chart
components.description: Creates a PDF barchart visualization of sales data using matplotlib and saves it to /tmp/sales_chart.pdf.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful creation of the CSV report.

connections.purpose: Read CSV and write PDF chart

components.name: Email Sales Report
components.description: Emails the CSV sales report and PDF chart to the management team with a dateparameterized subject line.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after both CSV and PDF files have been successfully created.

description.default: Sequential linear pipeline that generates daily sales reports by querying PostgreSQL sales data, converting it to CSV, creating a PDF chart, and emailing the report to management.

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

partitioning.description: Data partitioning strategy (e.g., daily, hourly, monthly)

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

postgres_conn_id.description: Connection ID for the PostgreSQL database

provide_context.description: Flag to provide Airflow context to the Python callable
Flag to provide Airflow context to the Python callable

to.description: Recipient email address for the sales report

subject_template.description: Email subject line template, parameterized with execution date ({{ ds }})

files.description: List of file paths to attach to the email

sources: PostgreSQL sales table (daily aggregated sales data)
sinks: Email sent to management with CSV and PDF attachments
